  - In the Linux kernel, the following vulnerability has been resolved: ext4: fix slab-use-after-free in
    ext4_split_extent_at() We hit the following use-after-free:
    ================================================================== BUG: KASAN: slab-use-after-free in
    ext4_split_extent_at+0xba8/0xcc0 Read of size 2 at addr ffff88810548ed08 by task kworker/u20:0/40 CPU: 0
